attributes.title: Worst Leader of The Free World
attributes.review: There is absolutely zero possibility that I will vote this most inept, incompetent, racist, corrupt, disgusting, vile, inarticulate, illiterate, senile, piece of crap back in our White House a second term.  I will use EVERYTHING within me to make sure he is not re elected.  He has destroyed the US from the inside out.  We are a laughing stock around the world.  The world can’t believe that we let a retarded moron lead our once great nation.  Everything trump touches, he destroys.  He did this with his failed businesses by filing many bankruptcies and not paying his vendors their contracted agreement; and now his poor incompetent judgement has placed our nation in perils...high unemployment, low wage jobs, low/no benefits, a pandemic, zero education policies, skyrocketing cost of living, lack of protection for senior citizens, etc.  The absolutely worst possible creature to ever inhabit the White House.  Kick him out!!!
